text: Anke Jacobs (born 28 July 1987) is a South African water polo player. She competed for the South Africa women's national water polo team in the 2013 World Aquatics Championships and 2014 FINA Women's Water Polo World Cup. == References == == Other websites == * no-bar-too-high-as-jacobs-plays * sa- ladies-water-polo-squad-named Category:1987 births Category:Living people Category:South African water polo players
